1
00:00:53,371 --> 00:00:55,197
Apakah kamu baik-baik saja?

2
00:00:56,023 --> 00:00:59,443
Demam Anda naik hingga
39 derajat Celcius semalam.

3
00:00:59,443 --> 00:01:00,920
Masih sakit?

4
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:03,013
Apakah kamu ingin pergi ke rumah sakit?

5
00:01:04,983 --> 00:01:07,059
Mengapa kamu terlambat sekali?

6
00:01:09,887 --> 00:01:12,223
Kau tahu aku benci

7
00:01:12,223 --> 00:01:14,316
sedang menunggu seseorang.

8
00:01:17,854 --> 00:01:19,738
Sun Tae Hyung...

9
00:01:21,858 --> 00:01:23,617
Aku menyukaimu.

10
00:01:24,777 --> 00:01:26,453
Woo Hyun Jin.

11
00:01:29,724 --> 00:01:32,518
Itulah mengapa aku terus-menerus mendapati diriku
menunggumu.

12
00:01:34,746 --> 00:01:38,715
Kamu adalah segalanya bagiku yang pertama.

13
00:01:40,626 --> 00:01:43,971
Tidak pernah ada yang menungguku sampai larut malam,

14
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:47,658
atau pulang ke rumah saat aku menunggu mereka...

15
00:02:06,361 --> 00:02:08,537
Sepertinya ada seseorang di depan pintu.

16
00:02:14,435 --> 00:02:15,453
Tidak, tidak apa-apa.

17
00:02:15,453 --> 00:02:17,747
Ini berat, biar saya angkat.

18
00:02:17,747 --> 00:02:19,482
Ini, pegang ini.

19
00:02:19,482 --> 00:02:20,667
Dari mana semua ini berasal?

20
00:02:20,667 --> 00:02:23,962
Hanya beberapa lauk pendamping, bukan masalah besar.

21
00:02:23,962 --> 00:02:25,463
Beberapa sayuran hijau dan sayuran kering, tidak ada yang istimewa.

22
00:02:25,463 --> 00:02:26,506
Anda perlu makan dengan benar jika Anda membesarkan seorang anak.

23
00:02:26,506 --> 00:02:27,990
Sebenarnya kamu tidak perlu melakukan itu...

24
00:02:27,990 --> 00:02:29,467
Ibuku semakin tua, kau tahu,

25
00:02:29,467 --> 00:02:32,119
Jadi, dia selalu membuat terlalu banyak. Baiklah kalau begitu,

26
00:02:32,119 --> 00:02:34,498
Kalau begitu, aku akan membuangnya saja. Berikan padaku.

27
00:02:34,498 --> 00:02:35,537
Tunggu, bukan.

28
00:02:35,537 --> 00:02:36,999
Aku akan makan semuanya. Terima kasih banyak.

29
00:02:36,999 --> 00:02:38,459
Saya akan mengembalikan kontainer-kontainer itu dalam keadaan kosong.

30
00:02:38,459 --> 00:02:41,045
Oh, itu akan sangat menyenangkan.

31
00:02:41,045 --> 00:02:42,689
Apakah Woo Joo kecil sudah tidur?

32
00:02:42,689 --> 00:02:44,482
Ya ampun, memang benar.

33
00:02:44,482 --> 00:02:46,659
Sebaiknya aku jangan berisik.

34
00:02:47,777 --> 00:02:49,929
Bisakah kamu melihat menembus benda-benda itu?

35
00:02:49,929 --> 00:02:51,013
Kenapa pakai kacamata hitam di dalam ruangan...?

36
00:02:51,013 --> 00:02:53,015
Oh, lupakan saja itu.

37
00:02:53,015 --> 00:02:54,367
Jadi, ibu Bom memberitahuku...

38
00:02:54,367 --> 00:02:57,586
Kalian berdua bukan pasangan, tapi mertua?

39
00:03:00,457 --> 00:03:04,218
Villa ini tidak menyimpan rahasia sama sekali, sungguh.

40
00:03:09,991 --> 00:03:12,744
Ada apa dengan kalian berdua?

41
00:03:13,737 --> 00:03:14,763
TIDAK.

42
00:03:14,763 --> 00:03:16,264
Lalu, apa sebenarnya penyebab semua ketegangan ini?

43
00:03:16,264 --> 00:03:18,016
Ada sesuatu yang ingin kutanyakan padamu.

44
00:03:18,016 --> 00:03:19,184
- Terjadi sesuatu, kan?
- Kamu akan membangunkan Woo Joo.

45
00:03:19,184 --> 00:03:22,896
Dia terus menyuruhku untuk diam dan menyuruhku untuk tutup mulut.

46
00:03:22,896 --> 00:03:24,564
Pasti ada sesuatu yang terjadi, kan?

47
00:03:24,564 --> 00:03:26,306
Benar?

48
00:03:30,987 --> 00:03:32,409
Astaga.

49
00:03:32,409 --> 00:03:35,190
Benarkah aku baru saja mengatakan semua itu
sambil terlihat seperti ini?

50
00:03:44,275 --> 00:03:47,334
[Episode 6]

51
00:03:55,119 --> 00:03:58,372
Setidaknya kamu harus tidur dengan cukup.

52
00:04:32,698 --> 00:04:36,494
Seharusnya kau bilang padaku untuk tidak pergi
kalau kau sakit separah ini...

53
00:04:41,391 --> 00:04:44,151
Bahkan ketika saya meminta orang-orang untuk tetap tinggal,

54
00:04:44,772 --> 00:04:47,154
Mereka semua tetap pergi.

55
00:04:52,802 --> 00:04:55,204
Aku tidak akan pergi ke mana pun.

56
00:05:19,412 --> 00:05:21,539
Terima kasih sudah datang.

57
00:05:39,897 --> 00:05:42,209
Kamu sudah bangun?

58
00:05:43,060 --> 00:05:45,646
Kamu baik-baik saja? Apakah lidahmu terbakar?

59
00:05:54,881 --> 00:05:56,574
Bukan apa-apa.

60
00:05:56,574 --> 00:05:57,992
Saya harus segera berangkat kerja.

61
00:05:57,992 --> 00:05:59,511
Izinkan saya bersiap-siap dulu.

62
00:05:59,511 --> 00:06:01,763
Kamu hampir tidak tidur sama sekali, kan?

63
00:06:01,763 --> 00:06:02,788
Tidak, tidak apa-apa.

64
00:06:02,788 --> 00:06:04,557
Setiap kali suhu tubuh Anda naik semalaman,

65
00:06:04,557 --> 00:06:05,809
Aku sempat tidur sebentar di sela-sela itu.

66
00:06:05,809 --> 00:06:08,311
Aku sudah menyisakan bubur untukmu, jadi makanlah.

67
00:06:08,311 --> 00:06:09,871
Dan sebelum Anda pergi,

68
00:06:09,871 --> 00:06:11,064
jika kamu membawa Woo Joo ke tempat Bom,

69
00:06:11,064 --> 00:06:12,607
Aku akan menjemputnya saat aku pulang nanti.

70
00:06:12,607 --> 00:06:13,716
Satu hal lagi...

71
00:06:13,716 --> 00:06:15,076
Apa kamu sudah makan?

72
00:06:15,076 --> 00:06:16,093
Apa?

73
00:06:16,093 --> 00:06:18,012
Saya bertanya apakah Anda sudah makan.

74
00:06:18,905 --> 00:06:21,408
Tidak, saya akan membeli sesuatu di kantor.

75
00:06:21,408 --> 00:06:22,534
Aku harus pergi sekarang.

76
00:06:22,534 --> 00:06:24,251
Woo Joo, selamat tinggal.

77
00:06:38,532 --> 00:06:40,385
Aku menyukaimu.

78
00:06:40,385 --> 00:06:42,186
Woo Hyun Jin.

79
00:06:44,497 --> 00:06:47,208
Mengapa jantungku berdetak begitu cepat?

80
00:06:52,051 --> 00:06:53,064
Halo?

81
00:06:53,064 --> 00:06:55,299
Apakah ini wali dari Sun Woo Joo?

82
00:06:55,299 --> 00:06:57,676
Ya, itu saya. Ada apa?

83
00:06:57,676 --> 00:06:59,946
Halo, saya menelepon dari Tempat Penitipan Anak Saetbyeol.

84
00:06:59,946 --> 00:07:01,114
Saat ini kami memiliki lowongan.

85
00:07:01,114 --> 00:07:03,074
di kelas bayi kami dan ingin memberi tahu Anda.

86
00:07:03,074 --> 00:07:04,576
Oh, itu luar biasa!

87
00:07:04,576 --> 00:07:06,286
Kapan dia bisa datang?

88
00:07:06,286 --> 00:07:08,163
Jika itu nyaman bagi Anda,

89
00:07:08,163 --> 00:07:09,980
Dia dipersilakan datang hari ini.

90
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:12,750
Meskipun sudah agak siang, mampirlah
agar dia bisa bertemu dengan anak-anak lainnya.

91
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:15,044
dan mulailah merasa nyaman.

92
00:07:15,044 --> 00:07:16,379
Tentu, itu berhasil.

93
00:07:16,379 --> 00:07:17,947
Saya akan mempertimbangkan hal itu.

94
00:07:17,947 --> 00:07:19,507
Saya sangat menghargainya.

95
00:07:19,507 --> 00:07:21,350
Terima kasih.

96
00:07:22,326 --> 00:07:24,662
Aku perlu memberi tahu Tae Hyung tentang ini.

97
00:07:26,372 --> 00:07:27,798
Sebenarnya, tunggu dulu.

98
00:07:27,798 --> 00:07:30,609
Apakah terlalu cepat untuk menelepon sekarang?

99
00:07:40,133 --> 00:07:43,539
Kamu baru saja makan.

100
00:07:45,734 --> 00:07:48,919
Tatapan mata anak anjing itu tidak akan berhasil.

101
00:07:54,423 --> 00:07:56,294
Ini belum pernah terjadi padaku sebelumnya.

102
00:07:56,294 --> 00:07:59,763
Seseorang yang membuatkan bubur untukku saat aku sakit.

103
00:08:04,744 --> 00:08:08,080
Tunggu, apakah dia pergi tanpa makan?

104
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:10,333
hanya karena aku?

105
00:08:12,727 --> 00:08:15,321
- Benarkah?
- Ya.

106
00:08:16,689 --> 00:08:19,491
Apakah sesulit itu berada di dekatku?

107
00:08:23,756 --> 00:08:26,155
Apakah Anda keberatan membawa Woo Joo?

108
00:08:26,155 --> 00:08:28,284
Apakah kamu akan menitipkan anakmu ke tempat penitipan anak sebelum berangkat kerja hari ini?

109
00:08:28,284 --> 00:08:29,781
Tempat penitipan anak?

110
00:08:29,781 --> 00:08:32,489
Saya pernah mendaftarkan Woo Joo ke daftar tunggu sebelumnya,

111
00:08:32,489 --> 00:08:34,148
dan mereka baru saja menelepon dan mengatakan ada lowongan.

112
00:08:34,148 --> 00:08:36,116
Saya akan mengirimkan alamatnya kepada Anda.

113
00:08:38,277 --> 00:08:41,364
Dia masih bayi, bukan anak kecil.

114
00:08:45,393 --> 00:08:48,012
Baiklah, saatnya berpakaian.

115
00:08:48,012 --> 00:08:48,596
TIDAK!

116
00:08:48,596 --> 00:08:50,139
Berikan kakimu padaku.

117
00:08:50,139 --> 00:08:51,832
TIDAK.

118
00:08:51,832 --> 00:08:53,709
Baiklah.

119
00:08:56,437 --> 00:08:59,448
Butuh waktu 30 menit hanya untuk berpakaian?

120
00:09:07,348 --> 00:09:09,242
Oke, aku akan mengambilnya.

121
00:09:09,242 --> 00:09:11,585
Tunggu.

122
00:09:22,655 --> 00:09:25,321
Tempat ini lebih besar dari yang saya duga.

123
00:09:25,321 --> 00:09:28,219
[Senang bertemu denganmu! Selamat datang!]
Kamu akan baik-baik saja, kan?

124
00:09:28,219 --> 00:09:30,229
- Ya.
- Benarkah?

125
00:09:30,913 --> 00:09:32,557
Baiklah.

126
00:09:32,557 --> 00:09:34,892
Mari kita masuk ke dalam.

127
00:09:34,892 --> 00:09:36,144
Kamu Woo Joo, kan?

128
00:09:36,144 --> 00:09:37,353
Halo.

129
00:09:37,353 --> 00:09:38,605
- Sapa saya.
- Ayo, beri hormat.

130
00:09:38,605 --> 00:09:39,897
Letakkan tangan di perut, seperti itu.

131
00:09:39,897 --> 00:09:41,573
Ayo.

132
00:09:42,633 --> 00:09:44,760
[Tempat Penitipan Anak Saetbyeol]

133
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:47,155
Apakah Anda kebetulan adalah ayah Woo Joo?

134
00:09:47,155 --> 00:09:48,956
Ayahnya?

135
00:09:50,140 --> 00:09:51,409
Di mana Anda melihat...

136
00:09:51,409 --> 00:09:54,002
Aku hanya seorang paman.

137
00:09:55,907 --> 00:09:57,081
Mengerti.

138
00:09:57,081 --> 00:09:59,066
Jujur saja, kamu memang memberikan kesan seperti seorang paman.

139
00:09:59,066 --> 00:10:00,752
Baiklah kalau begitu,

140
00:10:00,752 --> 00:10:03,720
Bisakah Anda mencatat kontak darurat?

141
00:10:08,659 --> 00:10:11,002
[Kontak Darurat Penitipan Anak Saetbyeol]

142
00:10:17,876 --> 00:10:20,671
[Nama Anak: Sun Woo Joo]

143
00:10:20,671 --> 00:10:23,598
[Penjaga Sun Woo Joo, Sun Tae Hyung]

144
00:10:46,255 --> 00:10:47,865
Permisi.

145
00:10:47,865 --> 00:10:49,384
Satu hal sebelum Anda pergi,

146
00:10:49,384 --> 00:10:51,052
Katakan padanya sesuatu seperti, "Paman harus bekerja,

147
00:10:51,052 --> 00:10:52,512
Tapi kamu bermain dengan teman-temanmu di sini,

148
00:10:52,512 --> 00:10:53,429
dan aku akan segera kembali untukmu."

149
00:10:53,429 --> 00:10:54,972
Pastikan Anda mengatakan itu sebelum Anda pergi.

150
00:10:54,972 --> 00:10:56,766
Dengan begitu dia tidak akan terus
bertanya-tanya kapan kamu akan kembali,

151
00:10:56,766 --> 00:10:57,975
Dia tidak akan merasa cemas,

152
00:10:57,975 --> 00:11:00,144
dan itu memberinya rasa nyaman

153
00:11:00,144 --> 00:11:02,629
karena tahu kau akan kembali untuknya.

154
00:11:02,629 --> 00:11:04,424
Tentu.

155
00:11:38,433 --> 00:11:40,017
Benar.

156
00:11:40,017 --> 00:11:42,444
Dia tidak seharusnya dibiarkan menunggu
tanpa mengetahui kapan.

157
00:11:49,277 --> 00:11:52,162
Paman.

158
00:11:58,536 --> 00:12:00,796
- Hei.
- Ya.

159
00:12:05,405 --> 00:12:07,271
Woo Joe.

160
00:12:09,213 --> 00:12:13,478
Aku harus mencari uang
untuk membeli makanan dan popokmu, oke?

161
00:12:15,803 --> 00:12:18,264
Jadi,

162
00:12:18,264 --> 00:12:21,017
Bersantailah di sini dan bermainlah bersama teman-temanmu.

163
00:12:22,251 --> 00:12:24,426
Lalu Bibi akan datang menjemputmu.

164
00:12:24,426 --> 00:12:25,438
Oke?

165
00:12:26,088 --> 00:12:27,882
Tos.

166
00:13:13,809 --> 00:13:15,929
Apa ini?

167
00:13:15,929 --> 00:13:18,641
Perasaan hampa yang aneh ini.

168
00:13:23,228 --> 00:13:25,982
Aku lupa memberinya kabar terbaru.

169
00:13:26,887 --> 00:13:29,951
Woo Joo sudah mandi dan berganti pakaian,

170
00:13:30,947 --> 00:13:35,665
dan hari pertamanya di tempat penitipan anak telah selesai.

171
00:13:37,552 --> 00:13:39,752
Sepertinya aku juga harus mengiriminya foto.

172
00:13:40,847 --> 00:13:42,643
Yang ini?

173
00:13:44,934 --> 00:13:46,185
Apa-apaan ini...?

174
00:13:46,185 --> 00:13:46,894
Apa yang baru saja saya lakukan?

175
00:13:46,894 --> 00:13:48,229
Tidak, tidak.

176
00:13:48,229 --> 00:13:50,857
Bagaimana cara membatalkan pengiriman ini?

177
00:13:50,857 --> 00:13:53,294
Terlambat, dia menyadarinya.

178
00:13:53,294 --> 00:13:55,344
Apa ini?

179
00:13:55,344 --> 00:13:57,512
Ada apa?

180
00:13:57,512 --> 00:13:59,448
Ada apa dengan kalian berdua?

181
00:13:59,448 --> 00:14:02,001
Apakah kalian sudah bertukar foto selfie?

182
00:14:02,001 --> 00:14:03,369
tanpa memberitahuku?

183
00:14:03,369 --> 00:14:06,171
Jadi, ada kejadian lain yang terjadi, kan?

184
00:14:06,856 --> 00:14:09,066
Sebenarnya...

185
00:14:09,066 --> 00:14:11,276
Seseorang mengatakan bahwa mereka menyukaiku.

186
00:14:11,276 --> 00:14:12,336
Kamu serius?

187
00:14:12,336 --> 00:14:13,546
Dia mengaku?

188
00:14:13,546 --> 00:14:14,797
Dia melakukan itu?

189
00:14:14,797 --> 00:14:16,966
Sejak kapan segala sesuatunya menjadi secepat ini?

190
00:14:16,966 --> 00:14:18,259
Berikan saya semua detailnya.

191
00:14:18,259 --> 00:14:20,303
Lalu bagaimana reaksi Anda?

192
00:14:20,303 --> 00:14:23,097
Dia mungkin hanya linglung karena pengaruh obat-obatan.

193
00:14:23,097 --> 00:14:25,315
Demamnya sangat tinggi kemarin.

194
00:14:26,017 --> 00:14:28,085
Itu bukan pertanyaan saya.

195
00:14:28,085 --> 00:14:30,338
Aku ingin menanyakan tentang perasaanmu.

196
00:14:32,297 --> 00:14:33,691
Coba pikirkan,

197
00:14:33,691 --> 00:14:35,943
if you run into your first love again,

198
00:14:35,943 --> 00:14:38,654
wouldn't old feelings come back?

199
00:14:38,654 --> 00:14:41,014
That senior was your first love, right?

200
00:14:41,014 --> 00:14:43,951
Yeah, he was.

201
00:14:43,951 --> 00:14:45,852
And judging by how he treats you,

202
00:14:45,852 --> 00:14:48,856
he clearly still cares about you.

203
00:14:50,188 --> 00:14:51,959
Honestly, I can't tell.

204
00:14:51,959 --> 00:14:53,294
He's always been kind

205
00:14:53,294 --> 00:14:55,296
and considerate with everyone.

206
00:14:55,296 --> 00:14:56,839
Oh, come on.

207
00:14:56,839 --> 00:14:59,474
I bet it's just you he treats that way.

208
00:15:00,553 --> 00:15:02,637
And what about your in-law?

209
00:15:02,637 --> 00:15:04,138
Has he ever made you feel

210
00:15:04,138 --> 00:15:07,516
something different?

211
00:15:07,516 --> 00:15:09,443
Something different?

212
00:15:10,043 --> 00:15:12,721
I mean, if you put it that way...

213
00:15:14,637 --> 00:15:16,283
Hyun Jin...

214
00:15:17,676 --> 00:15:19,886
There have been moments, yeah.

215
00:15:19,886 --> 00:15:22,406
He appears when I least expect it

216
00:15:22,406 --> 00:15:24,975
and catches me off guard,

217
00:15:24,975 --> 00:15:28,062
and I find myself depending on him.

218
00:15:29,830 --> 00:15:31,631
Plus,

219
00:15:33,668 --> 00:15:37,345
he had his guard up at first, so I missed it,

220
00:15:38,411 --> 00:15:40,341
but deep down, he cares more than most

221
00:15:40,341 --> 00:15:42,642
and he's been through a lot.

222
00:15:44,411 --> 00:15:47,373
Once I saw that, it all made sense.

223
00:15:48,123 --> 00:15:49,458
I realized

224
00:15:49,458 --> 00:15:52,003
he's been lonely this whole time.

225
00:15:53,229 --> 00:15:54,504
And it hit me that

226
00:15:54,504 --> 00:15:57,258
we might be pretty similar.

227
00:15:59,218 --> 00:16:01,070
If you're thinking about him that much,

228
00:16:01,070 --> 00:16:02,435
then just say yes.

229
00:16:02,435 --> 00:16:03,388
What's holding you back?

230
00:16:03,388 --> 00:16:04,765
There is a problem.

231
00:16:04,765 --> 00:16:07,267
I've never once seen him that way.

232
00:16:07,267 --> 00:16:10,579
Then try looking at him differently.

233
00:16:10,579 --> 00:16:12,456
Seriously, you share a place

234
00:16:12,456 --> 00:16:13,541
with a man who has feelings for you,

235
00:16:13,541 --> 00:16:15,079
and you don't feel a single thing?

236
00:16:15,079 --> 00:16:17,302
How is that even possible?

237
00:16:18,111 --> 00:16:21,323
Unless your heart's already with your senior.

238
00:16:21,323 --> 00:16:23,159
My heart?

239
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:27,000
All I have room for right now is...

240
00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:33,502
Woo Joo and landing a full-time job.

241
00:16:33,502 --> 00:16:35,921
Those two things, that's it.

242
00:16:35,921 --> 00:16:36,939
You know that

243
00:16:36,939 --> 00:16:39,567
I can't afford to think
about anything else right now.

244
00:16:39,567 --> 00:16:40,592
I don't know about that.

245
00:16:40,592 --> 00:16:44,097
I think time will tell.

246
00:16:50,519 --> 00:16:53,581
[Woo Joo's all bathed and changed,
and his first day of daycare is a wrap.]

247
00:16:53,581 --> 00:16:56,091
She read it and didn't even reply?

248
00:16:58,568 --> 00:17:00,738
Let's just focus on work.

249
00:17:02,618 --> 00:17:04,224
Shall we head in?

250
00:17:05,742 --> 00:17:07,178
[Food Supply Overview]
We have direct deals

251
00:17:07,178 --> 00:17:08,620
with quality-verified suppliers

252
00:17:08,620 --> 00:17:10,765
along with several
alternative sources in place.

253
00:17:10,765 --> 00:17:12,224
That's great.

254
00:17:12,224 --> 00:17:15,561
GloMarket took interest in the K-food brand

255
00:17:15,561 --> 00:17:17,087
that's been developed with care over the years,

256
00:17:17,087 --> 00:17:19,102
which means we absolutely must secure

257
00:17:19,102 --> 00:17:20,483
top-tier raw materials.

258
00:17:20,483 --> 00:17:22,631
Of course, we'll make it happen.

259
00:17:22,631 --> 00:17:26,155
Let's call it a day on this meeting, then?

260
00:17:26,155 --> 00:17:28,039
Thank you all.

261
00:17:33,910 --> 00:17:37,215
The roads will be packed at this hour.

262
00:17:37,958 --> 00:17:39,168
Tell me about it.

263
00:17:39,168 --> 00:17:40,336
So I was thinking...

264
00:17:40,336 --> 00:17:42,345
What if we sneak off for a bit?

265
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:50,971
Can we order?

266
00:17:50,971 --> 00:17:52,539
Sure, go right ahead.

267
00:17:52,539 --> 00:17:55,125
One Strawberry Love Latte, extra whip,

268
00:17:55,125 --> 00:17:56,977
five rounds of java chips blended on top,

269
00:17:56,977 --> 00:17:58,437
with tons of chocolate drizzle,

270
00:17:58,437 --> 00:18:00,782
and finish it off with banana pudding.

271
00:18:00,782 --> 00:18:01,816
I'm sorry?

272
00:18:01,816 --> 00:18:03,575
Banana pudding.

273
00:18:06,303 --> 00:18:07,913
What is this?

274
00:18:07,913 --> 00:18:08,930
What else could it be?

275
00:18:08,930 --> 00:18:11,392
It's your signature order.

276
00:18:12,350 --> 00:18:14,370
I can't believe you still know that.

277
00:18:14,370 --> 00:18:16,396
How could I forget?

278
00:18:16,396 --> 00:18:18,415
They only have this latte during the season.

279
00:18:18,415 --> 00:18:19,708
So each year when it comes back,

280
00:18:19,708 --> 00:18:22,294
I'd walk by and you'd cross my mind.

281
00:18:22,294 --> 00:18:24,571
Whenever I'd see someone with one,

282
00:18:24,571 --> 00:18:27,086
I'd wonder if you'd had yours yet.

283
00:18:27,086 --> 00:18:30,035
And when it disappeared from the menu,

284
00:18:30,035 --> 00:18:31,954
I'd feel this little pang of sadness.

285
00:18:32,579 --> 00:18:35,541
Itulah mengapa semua orang jatuh cinta padamu.

286
00:18:36,372 --> 00:18:40,866
Aku belum pernah punya pacar
sejak kuliah.

287
00:18:40,866 --> 00:18:41,922
Ayo.

288
00:18:41,922 --> 00:18:44,030
Apa? Aku serius.

289
00:18:44,030 --> 00:18:44,999
Mengapa hal itu begitu sulit dipercaya?

290
00:18:44,999 --> 00:18:48,678
Hanya saja, kamu selalu disukai banyak orang,

291
00:18:48,678 --> 00:18:52,015
Jelas brilian, cakap, baik hati,

292
00:18:52,015 --> 00:18:54,852
dan yang terpenting, tinggi dan tampan...

293
00:18:56,745 --> 00:18:58,813
Berlangsung?

294
00:18:58,813 --> 00:19:01,067
Kenapa kamu tiba-tiba berhenti bicara?

295
00:19:02,150 --> 00:19:03,502
Karena kamu terus menggangguku,

296
00:19:03,502 --> 00:19:06,748
Saya mengucapkan hal-hal yang tidak saya maksudkan.

297
00:19:09,508 --> 00:19:11,088
Omong-omong.

298
00:19:11,088 --> 00:19:13,220
Bagaimana kabar si kecil?

299
00:19:13,220 --> 00:19:14,287
Dia bagus.

300
00:19:14,287 --> 00:19:16,469
Dia pergi ke tempat penitipan anak untuk pertama kalinya hari ini.

301
00:19:16,469 --> 00:19:17,499
Dia sudah dewasa, kan?

302
00:19:17,499 --> 00:19:20,543
Dia memang benar-benar seperti itu.

303
00:19:20,543 --> 00:19:23,046
Itu pasti melegakan.

304
00:19:23,046 --> 00:19:24,690
Memang benar.

305
00:19:24,690 --> 00:19:26,901
Saya merasa stres karena harus mengelola hal itu.

306
00:19:26,901 --> 00:19:29,431
tanpa mertua saya di sekitar.

307
00:19:29,431 --> 00:19:33,329
Kamu sudah tidak tinggal bersama mertua lagi?

308
00:19:33,329 --> 00:19:37,544
Awalnya kami hanya berencana untuk bersama
selama sebulan.

309
00:19:39,496 --> 00:19:41,255
Saya senang mendengarnya.

310
00:19:42,332 --> 00:19:43,399
Apa maksudmu?

311
00:19:43,399 --> 00:19:45,994
Sejujurnya, itu membuatku sedikit gelisah,

312
00:19:46,628 --> 00:19:49,347
mengetahui bahwa kamu tinggal bersama seorang pria.

313
00:20:00,976 --> 00:20:03,211
Inilah hal menarik tentang Amy Choo.

314
00:20:03,211 --> 00:20:07,323
Dia benci diganggu
saat inspirasi datang.

315
00:20:08,066 --> 00:20:10,485
Jadi jika dia tidak merespons,

316
00:20:10,485 --> 00:20:13,906
Itu artinya sesuatu yang besar sedang terbentuk di dalam pikirannya,

317
00:20:13,906 --> 00:20:15,873
jadi beri dia ruang.

318
00:20:17,201 --> 00:20:18,433
Sedangkan untuk pembuatan storyboard,

319
00:20:18,433 --> 00:20:20,579
Dia mengerjakannya semua dengan tangan terlebih dahulu.

320
00:20:20,579 --> 00:20:22,122
Mengetik semuanya setelahnya,

321
00:20:22,122 --> 00:20:24,441
Itu menjadi tanggung jawabmu.

322
00:20:24,441 --> 00:20:26,675
Ketika perbedaan pendapat kreatif muncul,

323
00:20:26,675 --> 00:20:28,629
Dia memulai percakapan dengan kata-kata kasar,

324
00:20:28,629 --> 00:20:31,764
dan kamulah yang harus mengelolanya.

325
00:20:32,615 --> 00:20:35,289
Set panggung, bakat, penataan gaya,

326
00:20:35,289 --> 00:20:37,137
tanpa memerlukan petunjuk langkah demi langkah,

327
00:20:37,137 --> 00:20:39,372
Kamu harus mencari tahu semuanya sendiri,

328
00:20:39,372 --> 00:20:42,996
Bersih dan memiliki insting yang tajam.

329
00:20:42,996 --> 00:20:44,002
Yang terpenting,

330
00:20:44,002 --> 00:20:47,022
Dia sangat pilih-pilih soal makanan yang dia konsumsi.

331
00:20:47,022 --> 00:20:50,359
jadi semuanya harus organik.

332
00:20:50,359 --> 00:20:52,319
Setengah jam setelah setiap makan,

333
00:20:52,319 --> 00:20:58,166
berikan dia vitamin A, B, C, D, E

334
00:20:59,718 --> 00:21:01,620
dengan jadwal bergilir,

335
00:21:01,620 --> 00:21:03,205
dan lengkapi sisanya dengan buah-buahan...

336
00:21:03,205 --> 00:21:04,915
Tunggu,

337
00:21:04,915 --> 00:21:08,468
Bukankah saya dipekerjakan sebagai asisten?

338
00:21:09,743 --> 00:21:10,754
Itu benar.

339
00:21:10,754 --> 00:21:12,172
Dan aku diharapkan melakukan semua itu?

340
00:21:12,172 --> 00:21:13,006
Sendirian?

341
00:21:13,006 --> 00:21:15,391
Apakah itu terlalu berlebihan untukmu?

342
00:21:16,093 --> 00:21:17,994
Aku bisa mengatasinya, tentu saja.

343
00:21:17,994 --> 00:21:19,763
Apa pun yang perlu dilakukan, saya akan melakukannya.

344
00:21:19,763 --> 00:21:20,681
Itulah yang ingin saya dengar.

345
00:21:20,681 --> 00:21:23,189
Ini tim Amy Choo yang sedang kita bicarakan.

346
00:21:23,189 --> 00:21:24,214
Asal kamu tahu,

347
00:21:24,214 --> 00:21:25,769
jika rencanamu adalah bermalas-malasan untuk sementara waktu

348
00:21:25,769 --> 00:21:27,896
dan memanfaatkan reputasi Amy Choo

349
00:21:27,896 --> 00:21:29,314
sebagai batu loncatan untuk dirimu sendiri...

350
00:21:29,314 --> 00:21:30,983
Saya tidak akan menerima pekerjaan itu.

351
00:21:30,983 --> 00:21:33,659
Bagi saya, peran ini adalah

352
00:21:35,220 --> 00:21:39,241
Ini juga kesempatan terakhirku.

353
00:21:39,241 --> 00:21:41,417
Kalau begitu, kita sepaham.

354
00:21:41,417 --> 00:21:42,435
Oh, satu hal lagi.

355
00:21:42,435 --> 00:21:44,020
Apakah kamu berhasil terhubung?

356
00:21:44,020 --> 00:21:45,706
Proposal yang Amy Choo minta kamu periksa itu?

357
00:21:45,706 --> 00:21:47,102
Saya sedang mengerjakannya sekarang,

358
00:21:47,102 --> 00:21:48,166
tetapi referensi visualnya tetap

359
00:21:48,166 --> 00:21:51,211
Perlu dilakukan pengecekan silang lebih lanjut,

360
00:21:51,211 --> 00:21:53,655
Jadi, saya akan merangkumnya dan melaporkan kembali
pada akhir hari.

361
00:21:53,655 --> 00:21:55,700
Aku mencintai

362
00:21:56,878 --> 00:21:58,768
sikap itu.

363
00:22:00,262 --> 00:22:02,980
Dia butuh kopi sekarang juga.

364
00:22:04,016 --> 00:22:05,976
Aku harus pergi.

365
00:22:05,976 --> 00:22:07,985
Aku terlambat.

366
00:22:10,605 --> 00:22:14,200
Dia sangat setia padanya.

367
00:22:16,194 --> 00:22:18,037
Saya punya banyak sekali hal yang harus dikerjakan.

368
00:22:26,121 --> 00:22:27,964
Satu, dua.

369
00:22:30,709 --> 00:22:32,336
Berikan aku sesuatu yang malu-malu, malu-malu.

370
00:22:32,336 --> 00:22:34,095
Nah, itu dia, malu-malu.

371
00:22:36,214 --> 00:22:39,016
Sekarang, ekspresi wajahmu terlihat cerah dan ringan.

372
00:22:43,722 --> 00:22:45,724
Tunggu sebentar.

373
00:22:45,724 --> 00:22:48,317
Dia mengatakan kepada saya bahwa dia hanya bekerja sebagai asisten.

374
00:22:48,960 --> 00:22:51,672
Foto-foto ini sungguh mengesankan.

375
00:22:58,987 --> 00:23:00,955
Kamu sudah menyelesaikan semuanya.

376
00:23:03,766 --> 00:23:04,910
[Kehidupan Sehari-hari Saya]

377
00:23:04,910 --> 00:23:08,497
Saya pikir mungkin saya mengirimnya terlalu cepat,

378
00:23:08,497 --> 00:23:11,424
tetapi dia berhasil melakukannya dengan baik sendirian.

379
00:23:12,632 --> 00:23:15,420
Aku merasa seolah-olah aku hampir tidak melakukan apa pun,

380
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:17,805
Namun, lihatlah dia, tumbuh begitu cepat.

381
00:23:19,299 --> 00:23:20,717
Woo Joe.

382
00:23:20,717 --> 00:23:22,118
Apakah penitipan anak menyenangkan hari ini?

383
00:23:23,282 --> 00:23:26,932
Apakah kamu pikir kamu bisa melakukannya lagi besok?

384
00:23:29,601 --> 00:23:30,936
Kamu mau pergi ke mana?

385
00:23:30,936 --> 00:23:32,695
Woo Joo, kamu mau pergi ke mana?

386
00:23:36,775 --> 00:23:38,360
Kamu sudah kembali?

387
00:23:38,360 --> 00:23:40,320
Ya, aku kembali.

388
00:23:40,320 --> 00:23:41,780
Woo Joo juga ada di sini?

389
00:23:42,989 --> 00:23:45,412
Aku menjemputnya dalam perjalanan pulang kerja.

390
00:23:45,412 --> 00:23:46,910
Jadi begitu.

391
00:23:46,910 --> 00:23:47,994
Apakah kamu sudah makan?

392
00:23:47,994 --> 00:23:49,712
Ya, aku sudah makan.

393
00:23:50,622 --> 00:23:52,332
Oh, bagus. Baik.

394
00:23:52,332 --> 00:23:54,376
- Biar saya mulai mencuci...
- Sudah selesai.

395
00:23:54,376 --> 00:23:56,128
Jangan khawatir soal itu.

396
00:23:56,128 --> 00:23:58,004
Ah, benarkah?

397
00:23:58,004 --> 00:23:59,047
Aku yakin kita kekurangan deterjen...

398
00:23:59,047 --> 00:24:01,891
Jadi saya membelinya dalam perjalanan pulang.

399
00:24:07,931 --> 00:24:10,225
Sejujurnya,

400
00:24:10,225 --> 00:24:11,268
Bagaimana saya harus menjelaskannya?

401
00:24:11,268 --> 00:24:12,853
Kamu luar biasa, sungguh luar biasa.

402
00:24:14,003 --> 00:24:15,840
Terima kasih.

403
00:24:16,565 --> 00:24:17,899
Terima kasih banyak.

404
00:24:17,899 --> 00:24:19,669
Woo Joo, Tante itu yang terbaik, kan?

405
00:24:22,696 --> 00:24:24,072
Saya mau ke kamar mandi dulu.

406
00:24:24,072 --> 00:24:25,449
Ya, semoga harimu menyenangkan...

407
00:24:25,449 --> 00:24:27,291
Hati-hati di jalan.

408
00:24:33,206 --> 00:24:36,008
Apakah aku baru saja mengatakan "semoga perjalananmu menyenangkan"?

409
00:24:42,674 --> 00:24:45,302
Aku sungguh

410
00:24:45,302 --> 00:24:47,679
Perlu diperbaiki.

411
00:24:47,679 --> 00:24:49,313
Woo Joo, selamat tinggal.

412
00:24:50,474 --> 00:24:52,400
Saya mau ke kamar mandi dulu.

413
00:25:04,529 --> 00:25:05,530
Halo?

414
00:25:05,530 --> 00:25:06,865
Halo.

415
00:25:06,865 --> 00:25:08,582
Oh, benar.

416
00:25:10,619 --> 00:25:12,211
Ya.

417
00:25:12,954 --> 00:25:14,289
Ya.

418
00:25:14,289 --> 00:25:17,209
Kenapa banyak sekali ucapan "ya, ya"?

419
00:25:17,209 --> 00:25:18,293
Permisi.

420
00:25:18,293 --> 00:25:20,837
Perbaikan di apartemen Anda telah selesai.

421
00:25:20,837 --> 00:25:22,214
Semuanya sudah diperbaiki,

422
00:25:22,214 --> 00:25:24,466
jadi silakan datang dan lihat, dan jika semuanya sesuai,

423
00:25:24,466 --> 00:25:26,551
Anda bisa langsung pindah kembali.

424
00:25:26,551 --> 00:25:27,552
Omong-omong,

425
00:25:27,552 --> 00:25:30,597
Bagaimana kamu bisa menyelesaikannya secepat itu?

426
00:25:30,597 --> 00:25:32,265
Apakah ini sudah dilakukan dengan benar?

427
00:25:32,265 --> 00:25:33,391
Kaulah orangnya

428
00:25:33,391 --> 00:25:35,185
yang terus menyuruhku untuk bergegas, ingat?

429
00:25:35,185 --> 00:25:37,354
Lagipula, sudah hampir sebulan berlalu.

430
00:25:37,354 --> 00:25:38,980
Jadi, saya tidak yakin apa masalahnya.

431
00:25:38,980 --> 00:25:41,782
Baiklah, aku akan mampir dan melihatnya besok.

432
00:25:48,389 --> 00:25:51,826
[Hari Aku Pulang]

433
00:25:51,826 --> 00:25:54,645
Benarkah sudah satu bulan penuh berlalu?

434
00:25:54,645 --> 00:25:57,157
Ke mana perginya semua waktu itu?

435
00:26:05,506 --> 00:26:09,164
Saya baik-baik saja melakukan ini sendiri.

436
00:26:12,990 --> 00:26:15,212
Aku serius.

437
00:26:18,586 --> 00:26:21,131
Apa yang kukatakan padamu,

438
00:26:21,131 --> 00:26:23,678
Semua itu nyata.

439
00:26:25,756 --> 00:26:27,967
Namun,

440
00:26:27,967 --> 00:26:29,135
Aku tidak akan

441
00:26:29,135 --> 00:26:31,395
mengharapkan apa pun darimu.

442
00:26:32,555 --> 00:26:35,349
Aku hanya ingin kau tahu di mana posisiku.

443
00:26:35,349 --> 00:26:38,394
Saya tidak mencoba memaksakan sesuatu,

444
00:26:38,394 --> 00:26:40,479
dan aku tidak akan pernah

445
00:26:40,479 --> 00:26:42,276
Ini akan menyulitkanmu.

446
00:26:42,276 --> 00:26:44,320
Sejujurnya, aku sudah menduga

447
00:26:44,320 --> 00:26:46,406
Kamu mengoceh karena pengaruh obat.

448
00:26:46,406 --> 00:26:48,826
dan hampir tidak sadar.

449
00:26:50,031 --> 00:26:53,476
Berpura-pura tidak merasakan apa pun

450
00:26:53,476 --> 00:26:54,827
dan membiarkannya begitu saja,

451
00:26:54,827 --> 00:26:56,867
Itu bukan sesuatu yang bisa saya lakukan.

452
00:26:56,867 --> 00:26:59,256
Saya yakin itu langsung terlihat.

453
00:27:00,416 --> 00:27:02,426
Jadi,

454
00:27:03,127 --> 00:27:05,671
mari kita pertahankan saja

455
00:27:05,671 --> 00:27:08,007
seperti apa adanya mereka.

456
00:27:08,007 --> 00:27:09,508
Melihat?

457
00:27:09,508 --> 00:27:10,843
Woo Joo sudah tahu

458
00:27:10,843 --> 00:27:12,477
Suasananya berbeda.

459
00:27:13,679 --> 00:27:15,518
Kamu benar.

460
00:27:15,518 --> 00:27:17,939
Woo Joo memperhatikan semuanya.

461
00:27:21,145 --> 00:27:23,530
Tunggu sebentar, itu apa?

462
00:27:25,132 --> 00:27:26,992
Tas saya.

463
00:27:29,984 --> 00:27:32,038
Aku tidak menyukaimu.

464
00:28:03,145 --> 00:28:04,605
Ada apa?

465
00:28:04,605 --> 00:28:07,024
Mama.

466
00:28:07,024 --> 00:28:08,025
Mama.

467
00:28:08,025 --> 00:28:09,568
- Woo Joo.
- Ada apa?

468
00:28:09,568 --> 00:28:12,029
- Kemarilah padaku.
- Ibu.

469
00:28:12,029 --> 00:28:13,698
Mama.

470
00:28:13,698 --> 00:28:15,616
Tidak apa-apa.

471
00:28:15,616 --> 00:28:17,459
Mama.

472
00:28:20,166 --> 00:28:21,627
Aku terlambat.

473
00:28:21,627 --> 00:28:23,355
Tas saya.

474
00:28:24,375 --> 00:28:25,751
Di mana dompetku?

475
00:28:25,751 --> 00:28:27,461
Itu ada di atas rak mainan.

476
00:28:27,461 --> 00:28:29,095
Terima kasih.

477
00:28:33,050 --> 00:28:34,552
Kartu identitas, telepon.

478
00:28:34,552 --> 00:28:36,144
Tepat di sini.

479
00:28:37,365 --> 00:28:38,392
